high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the stove top, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the apple on the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the apple in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Put the apple in the microwave and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Pick up the apple on the counter to the left of the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Place the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and move toward the kitchen counter, then turn right and go around the kitchen counter, then turn right to go to the sink.
Pick up the apple on the counter to the left of the sink.
Clean the apple in the sink.
Turn to the left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, then close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple in the microwave.
